FragPunk, the exciting FREE-TO-PLAY 5v5 rule-breaking hero shooter launches on Xbox Series X|S on March 6th, unleashing countless possibilities with Shard Cards, powerful gameplay modifiers that let you break the rules of every round. 

The FragPunk Pioneer Bundle features a Premium Battle Pass voucher, platform-exclusive “X-Warrior” weapon skins along with charm and stickers.

The Xbox FragPunk Pioneer Bundle is ONLY available before game launches. Pre-Order Now!
